  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I was at the corner only sitting, so they never asked me for something without talking and talking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was, at this time, in my civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was so hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them, they dealed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "For one piece of bread, they took one shirt, and they get me wrong, better in, in wrong equality.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I, I could give everything only to-- but even these small pieces of bread never filled me my-- my stomach.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In my cell, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't see-- in Torun, I didn't see, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later, yes, later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Torun, I didn't see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our time was only morning for 20 or 15 minutes to run, to take a fresh air, to make the [INAUDIBLE] walk, walk, the walking.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then again, to the cell and sitting-- I don't know why without job, without nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, I'll never forget also this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was 5th December, 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The door was open, and the [GERMAN] called me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Come on, he said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He gave me also this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he took me not in the street, only from this prison to the judgment that was-- later, I have seen it was a judge house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had a special way, under way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Probably, this way is still now in Torun, because this judge house and this prison is still, is still standing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When they took me to this, to this judgment, to this judgment house, I looked.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Behind me was mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was this Heil Hitler, you know, these [INAUDIBLE], banner with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And five or six members of this in black dressing-- so not Gestapo, only just-- it's a judge, like judges.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "First, they stated my whole-- how I was born, where I was living, when I this.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
